Rema – Lady Mavin Records wonder boy, Rema drops his highly anticipated EP tagged ‘Bad Commando‘. Off the beautiful body of work, we bring you this masterpiece which he titled “Lady“. Just like his popular hit record ‘Demebi‘, ‘Lady‘ is another suspicious tune we should all watch out for. In fact, it is the Dumebi of this new EP. SEE ALSO: Rema – Spaceship Jocelyn The record is housed under the ‘Bad Commando‘ EP alongside three other beautiful tracks which were titled ‘Spaceship Jocelyn‘, ‘Rewind‘ and ‘Bad Commando‘. Check it out and share your thoughts below! ITUNES/APPLE MUSIC The post Rema – Lady appeared first on Latest Naija Nigerian Music, Songs & Video – Notjustok. Source: NotJust okay